Package: lexis
Title: English Psycholinguistic Norms in a Unified Tidy Resource
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jay", "Timm", email = "jay.timm01@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Compiles ten English psycholinguistic rating-norm datasets (age of
    acquisition, concreteness, valence/arousal/dominance, body-object interaction,
    humor, socialness, Lancaster sensorimotor norms, gender connotation, iconicity,
    and the multi-dimension Glasgow Norms) as a tidy resource of rater-averaged norms,
    each with per-item standard deviations and rater counts. Lexical covariates
    (lexical-decision and naming latencies, SUBTLEX-US and wordfreq word frequencies,
    WordNet sense counts) and GloVe word embeddings are provided alongside, with
    per-study participant provenance. Includes utility functions for lookup, search,
    filtering, embedding-based neighbor search, and stimulus matching.
